# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# Rule syntax:   <source>   <destination>   <status>
# status=200  → rewrite (URL stays, different file served)
# status=301  → permanent redirect (URL changes)
#
# The DE homepage shares index.html with / — language detection is
# done in JS based on location.pathname. Exact-match only so that inner
# DE pages (/de/biergarten-berlin/ etc.) keep serving their own index.html.
/de/    /index.html    200
/de     /de/           301

# Everything else: let Pages serve the file at the path (default behavior).
